Package camzup.core

Interface IUtils

All Known Subinterfaces:
ICurve, IEntity, IEntityData, IMaterial, IMesh
All Known Implementing Classes:
CamEntity2, CamEntity3, Curve, Curve2, Curve3, CurveEntity2, CurveEntity3, Entity, Entity2, Entity3, EntityData, Gradient, ImageEntity2, ImageEntity3, Material, MaterialAwt, MaterialPImage, MaterialSolid, MaterialUv, Mesh, Mesh2, Mesh3, MeshEntity2, MeshEntity3, Rng, TextEntity2, TextEntity3, Utils
public interface IUtils
Holds mathematical constants used by the rest of the library. Provides convenience functions for printing a hash code and identity hash code as hexadecimal strings.
